{% extends 'partials/base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Calcola la tua Carta Human Design Gratis | Valentina Russo{% endblock %}

{% block extra_css %}
<style>
  .carta-hd-wrap {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md);
  }
  .carta-hd-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .carta-hd-intro h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .carta-hd-intro p {
    color: var(--text-muted, #666);
    font-size: 1rem;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .carta-hd-widget {
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .carta-hd-cta {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #f5f0f8;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }
  .carta-hd-cta p {
    color: #555;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .carta-hd-cta a {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .carta-hd-cta a:hover { opacity: 0.88; }
</style>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="carta-hd-wrap">

  <div class="carta-hd-intro">
    <h1>{{ page.header.title }}</h1>
    <p>{{ page.header.description }}</p>
  </div>

  <div class="carta-hd-widget">
    <div id="asccalc-widget"></div>
    <script src="https://api.simplechartcalculator.com/widget.js?key={{ page.header.api_key }}&theme=light&font=Outfit&width=760&showcore=true&showplanets=true"></script>
  </div>

  <div class="carta-hd-cta">
    <p>Vuoi capire cosa significa davvero la tua carta? Valentina ti guida in una consulenza Human Design personalizzata.</p>
    <a href="/contatti">Prenota una consulenza con Valentina</a>
  </div>

</div>
{% endblock %}
